<template>
  <v-card
      class="mx-auto"
      max-width="800"
      height="400"
      margin="auto"
      color="#1b5e20"
  >
    <v-card-text>
      <v-container class="check">
      <v-checkbox label="Botaniste"></v-checkbox>
      <v-checkbox label="Utilisateur"></v-checkbox>

      </v-container>
    </v-card-text>

      <v-file-input class="img"
          label="File input"
          variant="filled"
          prepend-icon="mdi-camera"
      ></v-file-input>
    <v-textarea label="Label" variant="solo" class="text"></v-textarea>

  </v-card>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name:"DemandeGardinnage",

}
</script>
<style>
.mx-auto{
  color:white;

  margin-top: 100px;
}
.img{
  width:270px;
  margin:auto;
}
.check{
  display:flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-left:100px
}
.text{
  width:400px;
  margin:auto;
}
</style>
